metadata.name: Ace of Hearts as Elon Musk
metadata.description:
The Ace of Hearts playing card featuring a portrait of Elon Musk is the ultimate symbol of innovation and ambition. 

The bold red heart represents the passion and drive that Musk brings to everything he does, while the Ace symbolizes the pinnacle of success. The detailed portrait captures the intensity and determination in Musk's gaze, making this card a must-have for any fan of the visionary entrepreneur. 

Whether you're a collector or just looking for an interesting piece of art, this Ace of Hearts playing card is sure to impress.
